    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I noted that when you move units, they keep their force fire command which is not consistent with CNC Gold - the command queue was about 1 deep, where this appears to hold Force Fire + Any Move Orders. Fun bonus - this allows a unit to force fire on the ground, then move to where its force-firing, and shoot itself to death."
